article.linkText: Crowley scores 30 as Southern Miss downs Old Dominion 78-73
article.story: HATTIESBURG, Miss. -- — Austin Crowley's 30 points led Southern Miss over Old Dominion 78-73 on Wednesday night. Crowley added 11 rebounds for the Golden Eagles (13-11, 7-5 Sun Belt Conference). Donovan Ivory scored 16 points and added eight rebounds. Victor Iwuakor shot 4 of 7 from the field and 4 for 9 from the line to finish with 12 points, while adding 11 rebounds and five blocks. The Monarchs (6-18, 2-11) were led in scoring by Chaunce Jenkins, who finished with 22 points. Tyrone Williams added 17 points, nine rebounds and five steals for Old Dominion. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
